values: I am sick and tired of people wanting to know who I like so much. Sometimes, I don't even like someone, and they still pry for me to answer. And when i answer they don't beleive me. Fucking leave me alone, I don't care about your life so god damn much, and it's none of you rbusiness to begin with! So if I like someone, quite criticizing and freaking out... damn preps

You are a temptress

IT'S FINALLY OVER, NO MORE GRIFFIN. YAY!

What's up? Today I walked, talked, but I didn't f*ck, that was just for effect! Anyways, Joey, Justin, and I walked all over The Colony, and now I am at Pirate's spending the night...All week, parents going out of town *CELEBRATION* maybe I won't get yelled at this week? Hmmm, sounds good to me!
I swear, I am in love. And it is the best feeling ever!

Nothing happened today. There was supposed to be a big fight today, but it ended before it started. Surprise? Not really, it was obvious that Ms. Williams would find out about that, duh! Stupid idiots!

Well, seems like I'm a bitch! YAY! A few 7th graders that i have never met randomly called me a bitch. Eh, maybe they're right! But after all, I did get to go to Six Flags on Friday and they went to The Zoo, I rest my case! Talk later about any developments...?

Aubz is having a party today. Originally it is her brother's b-day party, but Aubz got to invite some of her friends too.

Geez, I am so freaking tired. My back hurts, my eyes are barely open, and I am breaking out. Someone shoot me, I feel bad. But yet, I feel ok. I hate this.

I am going to start writing in this again. Why? I do not know, I just want something else to do on the computer so that I can have an excuse to stay on. But I don't think I could say, "Mom I need to update all of my journals online!" when mother has to do the bills right? Either way, I will find a way on.

Anywayz, TAKS is over (thank goodness) and Six Flags is tomorrow! YEAH!!!!

That's all the updates right now. I will start to type in this regularly, I PROMISE!

+Cryss+

UH, if you want to read up on me, go to my Xanga, I feel more comfortable there!

http://www.xanga.com/cryss2jinx
I am supposed to be cleaning my room, but I am too tired. My parents are seeing 50 First Dates. i bet my mom won't get grounded if she doesn't call me by nine. God damn bitch...

OMG! Levi and I were at the movies and it was sooo amazing. I will never forget that night! We made out and it was soo real! I am soo in love with him and he says that he is really in love with me. he even gave me a promise ring. I am in love with him, even though I am only 14!

Today I have gotten one rose and 6 snickers. I got Levi Sliknot - Iowa and an awesome barbed wire necklace. From what he has told me, and his friends, he has gotten me a $100 necklace. He is going to give it to me tonight. I am going to cry! I love him so much!
I am in the middle of second period right now. Damn these keyboards f*cking suck! I can't wait until tomorrow. It is gonna be so freaking awesome g2g...write later byez...
Blah day...Tired...At Pirate's house...Like it here...Hate it at home...turtle turtle.

He he...my mom let me stay home today becuase I didn't have my homework. Pirate is supposed to bring me my homework to me after school today. This rocks! I get to do nothing ALL day! Life is soooooooooo sweeeeeet right now!

When I was at Pirate's house and we were about to go to the SMu trip, I was really sick. I ignored it htough, because I din't want to miss the trip. As the day went on I got sicker and sicker. When I got home, I was so sick I had to cancel the date with me and Levi :(. I was so pissed. Levi told me I should get some rest and that he loved me anyway. So I passed out. At the SMU trip my group was the only group who won out of the whole school. We won $500 for the school. Mrs. Thompson was pissed because she was the science teacher and her group didn't win! lol. It was so cool though. Pirate, Jeremy, Justin, and I were all in the same group. I wish levi was there he would've loved it. Well my tylenol is kicking in. I didn't realize unitl after I took the 4 pills that the bottle said 'may cause drowziness". In other words, I picked up the wrong bottle. Thats how sick i am...:(

I am extremely tired, but I cannot go to sleep....

The SMU trip is tomorrow/today. I can't wait. And also Levi and I are going to the mall with Joey and her boyfriend, Vamp. I will write and say what happens at both, Byez...

-Cryss
